sections.heading: Install
sections.text:
macOS
:
Download
the
.dmg
file or run
brew cask install netron
Linux
:
Download
the
.AppImage
or
.deb
file.
Windows
:
Download
the
.exe
installer.
Browser
:
Start
the browser version.
Python Server
: Run
pip install netron
and
netron [FILE]
or
import netron; netron.start('[FILE]')
.
